flowchart TD
    R[Register / Login] --> SA[Supabase Auth]
    SA --> EM{Email confirmed?}
    EM -->|No| VE[/verify-email/]
    EM -->|Yes| EP[ensure_profile_from_auth RPC]
    EP --> PR[profiles row]
    EP --> US[users row + walletBalance]
    PR --> G{Route guard}
    G -->|suspended| SU[/suspended/]
    G -->|not approved| PA[/pending-approval/]
    G -->|ok| APP[Protected routes]
